                h3(style="font-family:'Segoe UI';") #{learner.name}, You have a new assignment!
                p(style="font-family:'Sf UI';") We've attached the link to assignment allocated to you by instructor #{allotedBy}.
                div(style="text-decoration: none; list-style-type: none;font-family: 'Segoe UI';")
                    h5(style='margin: 5px 0px;')
                        | Assignment No.:   
                        span(style='color:#d9a34a; font-size: 12px;') #{assignment.unitNo}
                    h5(style='margin: 5px 0px;')
                        | Assignment Title: 
                        span(style='color:#d9a34a; font-size: 12px;') #{assignment.title}
                    h5(style='margin: 5px 0px;')
                        | Deadline:         
                        span(style='color:#d9a34a; font-size: 12px;') #{prettyDate(learner.duedate)}
                a(href=allotmentUrl style='display: flex; background-color: #007AC2; color: #fff; padding: 10px 0; text-decoration: none; padding-left: 45%; border: none; outline: none; cursor: pointer;') View
